This paper deals with face detection and clustering in movies, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also introduces a novel clustering method and verification system, which involves machine learning techniques such as ranking and classification, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation metric for the end-to-end system, which involves measuring the accuracy of the system, making it relevant to cryptography and security (cs.CR) category.
